00%","height":"380","src":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nqOSznyJ7aU?rel=0","title":"YouTube video","frameBorder":"0","allow":"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture","allowFullScreen":true,"style":{"borderRadius":"var(--r-2)","marginBottom":"var(--sp-2)","border":"none"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"rich","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"<h2>The Announcement</h2>\n<p>Microsoft в— the company that poured billions into OpenAI в— just launched <strong>three fully in-house foundational models</strong>. Not wrappers. Not fine-tunes. Built from scratch.</p>\n<p>Mustafa Suleyman called it the first salvo from Microsoft's superintelligence team and said renegotiating the OpenAI contract <strong>\"unlocked Microsoft's ability to pursue superintelligence\"</strong>.</p>\n<h3>MAI-Transcribe-1</h3>\n<p>Lowest word error rate across 25 languages. Beats Whisper, GPT-Transcribe, and Gemini 3.1 Flash-Lite. Runs at 2.5x current Azure speed. Pricing: $0.36/hr.</p>\n<h3>MAI-Voice-1</h3>\n<p>Generates 60 seconds of audio in under one second. Custom voice cloning from a 10-second sample.</p>\n<h3>MAI-Image-2</h3>\n<p>Ranked #3 on Arena.ai. Rolling into Copilot Voice, Teams, Bing, and PowerPoint.</p>\n"}}],""]}],["$","footer",null,{"className":"foot","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"foot-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"foot-brand","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"foot-logo","children":["silicon",["$","span",null,{"children":"feed"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"One place for all technology news. Built by people who work in tech, tired of checking 30+ tabs every morning."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"foot-col","children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"Topics"}],["$","$L10",null,{"href":"/tag/ai","children":"AI & Machine Learning"}],["$","$L10",null,{"href":"/tag/startups","children":"Startups & Funding"}],["$","$L10",null,{"href":"/tag/hardware","children":"Hardware & Chips"}],["$","$L10",null,{